    "pp.reta.faq7a": "Retatrutide protocol pricing reflects the additional clinical requirements: extended initial consultation, comprehensive metabolic workup, more frequent monitoring appointments, and active follow-up throughout. Pricing is disclosed at your first appointment. We do not publish price lists. Contact us via WhatsApp or email to schedule your consultation and receive a pre-consult overview of what the protocol involves.",

